{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_02_05",
  "title": "いつも\nみんなの\nそばに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、なんだかギョっと疲れが出てきたわ\nこれでBIGGYO問題も一件落着ってとこかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~‚ I feel completely gyotted out.\nI guess this settles the BIGGYO issue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 11.923696136499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね！　無事に魚魚っとさんを海に帰せて\nよかったよ。また魚魚っとさんと一緒に何かしたいギョ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right! I'm glad we were able to safely return Gyogyo-tto-san\nto the sea. I’d love to do something with him again‚ gyo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1333333333,
      "endTime": 22.5768031438,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15500.000000000002
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 17586.7902706
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "さすがさくらね。私はしばらくはごめんだわ……\nあ、{user}さん！　おかえりなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Sakura. I’ll pass for a while…\nAh‚ {user}-san! Welcome back!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7666666667,
      "endTime": 32.1525850932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが星見漁港に囚われたせいで\nこころ達はすギョク大変な目にあったんですよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because {user}-kun was captured at Hoshimi Fishing Port‚\nKokoro had to Gyo through tough times‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3666666667,
      "endTime": 39.4004537265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私達は{user}さんの命の恩人と言っても\n過言ではありませんわ！　感謝してくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s no exaggeration to say that\nwe’re {user}-san’s lifesavers! Be grateful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "endTime": 47.2110432625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "なんか{user}さんの様子が変じゃない？\nあの……大丈夫ですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t something strange about {user}-san?\nUm… are you okay…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4,
      "endTime": 54.655260753600004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ギョ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyo?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6333338421,
      "endTime": 56.5080277007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ギョギョーーーーーッ！？！？！？！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gyogyo~~~~~?!?!?!?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7000005087,
      "endTime": 59.9663951716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "gyogyo",
      "speakerName": "魚魚っとさん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Gyogyoto-san",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-gyogyo.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_02_05-gyogyo001.m4a",
      "text": "いつもみんなのそばに～ギョギョっと現れる～\nギョギョット！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Always by everyone’s side‚ appearing with a Gyogyo-tto!\nGyogyo-tto!",
        "id": ""
      },
